data.description: Step into your elegant 4-bedroom Colonial home, nestled in a highly desirable development within the Wallkill School District. Built in 2016, this meticulously crafted residence presents 2.5 bathrooms and a plethora of upscale features that will surely captivate you. Prepare to be wowed as you enter the heart of the home a stunningly designed kitchen that will captivate you with its marble countertops, enhanced by pendant lighting that gracefully illuminates the spacious island, complete with a convenient bar seating area. Adorned with a charming backsplash and boasting a custom-built beverage bar with Spalted maple cabinets and a marble countertop, this kitchen is a delight for everyday living and entertaining. Step through the sliders to the expansive 14 x 30 Trex deck, a true outdoor oasis that beckons for al fresco entertaining. Built in 2023, this deck is adorned with atmospheric outdoor lighting, perfect for hosting evening gatherings with friends and family. The underneath was crafted with Trex waterproofing and boasts 3 fans with 10 recessed lights (controlled by the same app as lighting up top) as well as a Bose outdoor sound system on the upper and lower level. Entertain in style within the formal dining room, featuring exquisite shiplap detailing that adds a touch of rustic charm to the space. Oak hardwood floors grace the main level, exuding warmth and sophistication throughout. Bask in the abundant natural light that floods the spacious living room, complete with an eye-catching accent wall adorned with shiplap and a fireplace with a stone accented mantle. French doors lead you into a versatile room, currently serving as an office haven. Marvel at the built-in wall units, featuring a magnificent live-edge desk crafted from rare Spalted maple, complete with tiger maple cabinetry. Boasting electronic ventilation systems and ample storage space, this office is a haven for productivity and creativity. Ascend the stairs to the spacious upper level, where new oak hardwood floors lead you to the generously sized master bedroom. Indulge in the beautiful ensuite bathroom, featuring a jacuzzi tub, a tiled shower, porcelain tile floors, quartz countertops, and cherry vanity cabinets. A spacious walk-in closet provides ample storage for your wardrobe essentials, ensuring that every day begins and ends in absolute comfort. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms and a full bathroom with a tiled tub/shower offer plenty of space for family and guests, while a conveniently located laundry room on the second floor adds a touch of practicality to daily living. Find inspiration in the additional office space, boasting built-ins and porcelain tile flooring a versatile retreat for work or relaxation. Venture downstairs to the finished basement incorporating 500-600 sqft (included in total 3,108 sqft). Currently set up as a home gym, this versatile space offers endless possibilities and boasts a walk-out to the patio area and yard, ideal for outdoor entertaining. Additional features include a 2-car garage with epoxy floors, a shed for extra storage, and a firepit with enchanting lighting for cozy evenings under the stars. Amenities abound, including central air, a security system, a whole house water filtration system, whole house humidifier that is hooked up to the furnace, gutter guards and a whole house water softener for added peace of mind. Enjoy the convenience of a great commuter location, just 23 minutes to Beacon Train Station, 15 minutes to I-84 and I-87, and 20 minutes to the vibrant Newburgh Waterfront, offering a plethora of dining options, including the renowned Hudson Taco. Explore the great outdoors with ease, with Minnewaska State Park and Mohonk Mountain House within 30 minutes. With its proximity to NYC, this idyllic retreat offers the perfect blend of luxury living and convenience. Don't let this opportunity slip away seize the chance to call this extraordinary residence your own.
